	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_SAM_RAILGUN">
			<Text>Railgun SAM</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_SAM_RAILGUN_HELP">
			<Text>Use Railgun SAM units to intercept enemy aircraft which are trying to attack nearby Units. Requires [ICON_RES_URANIUM] Uranium.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_SAM_RAILGUN_STRATEGY">
			<Text>The Railgun SAM unit is an upgrade to the Laser SAM unit, and provides an advancing army with anti-air defense. These units can intercept and shoot at enemy aircraft bombing targets within 3 tiles (but only one unit per turn). These units are fairly vulnerable to non-air attack and should be accompanied by infantry or armor.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_UNIT_SMAN_IEUP_SAM_RAILGUN_PEDIA">
			<Text>
				The Railgun SAM is a specialized anti-air unit, with enhanced capabilities to defend against enemy air attacks up to 3 tiles away. It is available on the discovery of Nuclear Fusion, and does not become obsolete. Requires [ICON_RES_URANIUM] Uranium.
			</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>	
	
